<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>ikdxhz的博客</title><link>https://ikdxhz.github.io</link><description>人类的伟大之处在于，即便身陷重重困境与艰难险阻，依然能够保持高贵而坚韧的姿态，展现出不屈不挠的精神风貌。这种崇高的品质不仅体现在面对逆境时的从容与优雅，更在于内心深处那份对尊严与信念的坚守。无论外界如何狂风暴雨，真正伟大之人总能以昂扬的姿态屹立，以无畏的勇气和深沉的智慧，书写属于自己的壮丽篇章。这种精神，正是人类在苦难中绽放的光辉，照亮前行的道路。</description><copyright>ikdxhz的博客</copyright><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/142083737?v=4</url><title>avatar</title><link>https://ikdxhz.github.io</link></image><lastBuildDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 14:31:15 +0000</lastBuildDate><managingEditor>ikdxhz的博客</managingEditor><ttl>60</ttl><webMaster>ikdxhz的博客</webMaster><item><title>HTML 小白入门教程：第二天，操，继续牛逼到飞起！</title><link>https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/HTML%20-xiao-bai-ru-men-jiao-cheng-%EF%BC%9A-di-er-tian-%EF%BC%8C-cao-%EF%BC%8C-ji-xu-niu-bi-dao-fei-qi-%EF%BC%81.html</link><description>操，兄弟，欢迎来到 HTML 学习的第二天！昨天你已经他妈的牛逼了一把，搞定了基本的网页骨架，写出了带标题、段落、图片和链接的页面，爽得不行吧？今天我们继续冲，不整那些高深莫测的玩意儿，保持简单粗暴，带你再学几个 HTML 的核心技能，顺便加点 CSS 基础，让你的网页从“能看”进化到“有点骚气”。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/HTML%20-xiao-bai-ru-men-jiao-cheng-%EF%BC%9A-di-er-tian-%EF%BC%8C-cao-%EF%BC%8C-ji-xu-niu-bi-dao-fei-qi-%EF%BC%81.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 14:30:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>HTML 小白入门教程：第一天，简单到他妈的爆炸，干货</title><link>https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/HTML%20-xiao-bai-ru-men-jiao-cheng-%EF%BC%9A-di-yi-tian-%EF%BC%8C-jian-dan-dao-ta-ma-de-bao-zha-%EF%BC%8C-gan-huo.html</link><description>操，欢迎来到 HTML 的世界，兄弟！这篇教程是为零基础的小白量身打造的，目标是让你在第一天就搞明白 HTML 的基本套路，写出个能看的网页。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/HTML%20-xiao-bai-ru-men-jiao-cheng-%EF%BC%9A-di-yi-tian-%EF%BC%8C-jian-dan-dao-ta-ma-de-bao-zha-%EF%BC%8C-gan-huo.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 12:51:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>HTML加载图标的终极指南：小白也能从零到牛逼，写法、原理、适配全他妈搞定！</title><link>https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/HTML-jia-zai-tu-biao-de-zhong-ji-zhi-nan-%EF%BC%9A-xiao-bai-ye-neng-cong-ling-dao-niu-bi-%EF%BC%8C-xie-fa-%E3%80%81-yuan-li-%E3%80%81-shi-pei-quan-ta-ma-gao-ding-%EF%BC%81.html</link><description>## 引言：加载图标是啥？为啥老子要学？

你打开个网页，啥也没加载出来，盯着空白屏幕像个傻逼等着外卖送到，结果外卖员还在路上！加载图标（Loading Icon）就是那个救命的玩意儿，告诉用户：“别他妈急，网页在干活，马上就好！”。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/HTML-jia-zai-tu-biao-de-zhong-ji-zhi-nan-%EF%BC%9A-xiao-bai-ye-neng-cong-ling-dao-niu-bi-%EF%BC%8C-xie-fa-%E3%80%81-yuan-li-%E3%80%81-shi-pei-quan-ta-ma-gao-ding-%EF%BC%81.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 12:27:08 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>熬夜的危害：别他妈拿命去赌</title><link>https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/ao-ye-de-wei-hai-%EF%BC%9A-bie-ta-ma-na-ming-qu-du.html</link><description>熬夜，你以为这是啥？证明你“努力”的勋章？还是“夜生活”的必备技能？别他妈做白日梦了！熬夜就是你亲手给自己下的毒，每晚刷手机、追剧、打游戏，你都在拿健康换那几小时的“爽”。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ikdxhz.github.io/post/ao-ye-de-wei-hai-%EF%BC%9A-bie-ta-ma-na-ming-qu-du.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 12:08:29 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>